TraitContainer
```c#
                   public int CalcSyncHash(ref int n)
                        {
                                ++Queries;
                                Actor last = null;
                                int ret = 0;
                                for (int i = 0; i < actors.Count; i++)
                                {
                                        Actor actor = actors[i];
                                        if (actor == last)
                                                continue;
                                        foreach (var syncHash in actor.SyncHashes)
                                                ret += n++ * (int)(1 + actor.ActorID) * syncHash.Hash;
                                        last = actor;
                                }
                                return ret;
                        }

```

Not very clean to pull in game logic into the container. But worth the performance improvement.

15 min ai multiplayer game played at max speed.

